---
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="/angle — Julien Klein">
  <div style="max-width: 680px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 1.5rem;">
    <div style="padding: 3rem 0 1rem;">
      <a href="/ressources" style="font-size: 0.85rem; color: #8B7355;">← Ressources</a>
    </div>
    <div style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;"><span style="font-family: monospace; font-size: 0.8rem; color: #5C7A4E; border: 1px solid #5C7A4E; padding: 0.2rem 0.6rem; border-radius: 999px;">Skill</span> <span style="font-family: monospace; font-size: 0.8rem; color: #8B7355; border: 1px solid #D4C9B5; padding: 0.2rem 0.6rem; border-radius: 999px;">Contenu</span></div>
    <h1 style="font-family: monospace; font-size: 1.8rem; margin: 0.5rem 0 1rem; color: #2C2416;">/angle</h1>
    <p style="font-size: 1.05rem; color: #8B7355; line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 2.5rem;">Trouve des angles éditoriaux forts en connectant des concepts du Garden. Parcourt le Second Brain, identifie les tensions, contradictions et parallèles inattendus, puis propose 5 angles avec le contre-intuitif en premier.</p>

    <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 2.5rem;">
      <div style="padding: 1.2rem; background: #FAF7F2; border: 1px solid #D4C9B5; border-radius: 10px;">
        <div style="font-size: 0.75rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.08em; color: #8B7355; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Pour qui</div>
        <div style="font-size: 0.9rem; color: #2C2416; line-height: 1.6;">Créateurs de contenu qui manquent d'idées ou qui publient toujours les mêmes angles. Le Skill mine ce que tu sais déjà.</div>
      </div>
      <div style="padding: 1.2rem; background: #FAF7F2; border: 1px solid #D4C9B5; border-radius: 10px;">
        <div style="font-size: 0.75rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.08em; color: #8B7355; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Prérequis</div>
        <div style="font-size: 0.9rem; color: #2C2416; line-height: 1.6;">Un Second Brain avec des notes. Plus il y a de matière, meilleurs sont les angles générés.</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2 style="font-size: 1rem; font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #2C2416;">Utilisation</h2>
    <div style="background: #2C2416; color: #F5F0E8; padding: 1.2rem 1.5rem; border-radius: 10px; font-family: monospace; font-size: 0.9rem; margin-bottom: 2rem; line-height: 1.8;">
      <div style="color: #8B7355; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;"># Sur un thème</div>
      <div>/angle TDAH</div>
      <br/>
      <div style="color: #8B7355; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;"># En croisant deux concepts</div>
      <div>/angle "Meta Ads × TDAH"</div>
      <br/>
      <div style="color: #8B7355; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;"># Libre (depuis le Second Brain complet)</div>
      <div>/angle</div>
    </div>

    <h2 style="font-size: 1rem; font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #2C2416;">Format de sortie</h2>
    <div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0;">
      {[
        "5 angles numérotés, contre-intuitif en premier",
        "Pour chaque angle : accroche courte (< 10 mots)",
        "Tension ou paradoxe exploité",
        "Notes du Second Brain qui alimentent l'angle",
        "Niveau de maturité (idée brute / à développer / prêt)"
      ].map((step, i) => (
        <div style="display: flex; gap: 1rem; align-items: baseline; padding: 0.7rem 0; border-top: 1px solid #D4C9B5;">
          <span style="font-size: 0.75rem; color: #8B7355; font-family: monospace; flex-shrink: 0;">{String(i+1).padStart(2,'0')}</span>
          <span style="font-size: 0.9rem; color: #2C2416;">{step}</span>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>

    <div style="margin-top: 3rem; padding-bottom: 5rem;">
      <div style="font-size: 0.8rem; color: #8B7355; margin-bottom: 1rem;">Skills liés</div>
      <div style="display: flex; gap: 1rem;">
        <a href="/ressources/skills/post-linkedin" style="font-family: monospace; font-size: 0.85rem; padding: 0.4rem 0.8rem; border: 1px solid #D4C9B5; border-radius: 6px; color: #2C2416;">/post-linkedin →</a>
        <a href="/ressources/skills/capture" style="font-family: monospace; font-size: 0.85rem; padding: 0.4rem 0.8rem; border: 1px solid #D4C9B5; border-radius: 6px; color: #2C2416;">/capture →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
